News.headline: FA Youth Cup: Luton Town v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.page_title: FA Youth Cup: Luton Town v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.URL_keywords: FA Youth Cup: Luton Town v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.short_description: The Daggers Academy are playing Luton Town away on Thursday 17th November in the second round of the FA Youth Cup.
News.description:
The game will be played at Kenilworth Road on Thursday 17th November with a 7:00pm kick off.

The Daggers beat Colchester United 7-3 at the Chigwell Construction Stadium while Luton Town defeated Barnet at the Hive 3-1 to progress from the first round.

Tickets will only be available for the main stand at Luton Town and the prices for the game: 
Adults: £3
Concessions: £1
